<br>
I know Salvaros loves his Emp sword, but IMO your next weapon upgrade should be GRMK. Or possibly some LDoN stuff if you can come up with something nice.  <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://dizzykid.homestead.com/files/GultSig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
