<br>
Much better than it looks on paper. And a hell of a lot more common than GRMK, at least for us. I think we're actually 1 GRMK out of ~20 kills... like Paf said, but a little worse. I'd take it over Jiva or Agnarr swords no question about it, the proc really is that good and procs a ton. Mallet from PoEarth might be worth looking forward to (and by the time you can kill Solusek, you'll be elemental capable), but the graphic is terrible. <p>[65 Deceiver] Marauder <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=50505&amp;resize=true">Dubb O`Boyce</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> &lt;Triune&gt;</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#1F0000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xanitamt>XanitaMT</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.geocities.com/uk_anime_fan/hellsing/alucard_tounge.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>QHills and Clueless</span><br>  Posts: 48<br> <font color=#AAAAAA>(10/21/03 1:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=39.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Weapon Choices...</span><hr size=1> Breaking down VT in order for you, taking gear into account, you want:<br>
<br>
Armguards of Shadows, 50 raw atk. Even better its Rogue/Ranger only, no sane reason to pass on this. As a rogue user I wouldnt use elemental over them. <br>
Aten neck for obvious reasons, so much better on an hybrid though. Dont take their shots at it if you can help it. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
Earring of FS = sick, still seen on the most high end rogues. Get two if you can and leave Erradication for warriors.  <br>
Crimson Runed Mask is godly by all accounts, but you have a nice mask and 50 AC is very warrior friendly, its also quite rare from what I've seen.<br>
Spiked Shoulderpads, weak spot of yours and those are very appreciable. <br>
Ring of the Crimson Bull. 250 hps until your sta maxes out..hurrah <br>
Cloudy Mark, guess you want a better bracer, from VT this is it. Not lore either unless I'm mistaken.<br>
Finally you have a nice selection of gloves to get, Atens are the best or the worse if you do poisons, Gloves of Warding give you massive saves and Sanguine some atk. I'd get warding given the choice but thats just me.<br>
<br>
As for the off hand, WS is nice if not for the proc. Your options are all a rangers wet dream... Take a close look at their weapons before getting agnarr's or AHB over them. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Remember banked gear does your guild no good. Planning ahead what you want does.<br>
-Xani <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#0E0E0E><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xanitamt>XanitaMT</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.geocities.com/uk_anime_fan/hellsing/alucard_tounge.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>QHills and Clueless</span><br>  Posts: 49<br> <font color=#AAAAAA>(10/21/03 6:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=39.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Weapon Choices...</span><hr size=1> Oops I thought that was a Midnight mantle on your shoulders, rubi aint weak at all I guess, didnt mean to diss your gear sorry.<br>
