<br>
I disagree with Xanita about Armguard, Elemental arms are just fine and easier to get than Aten arms. +ATK comes with time, and there are lots of options, particularly with LDoN being out now. And by the time you reach 200-250 worn atk you'll be kicking yourself for going with Aten arms over elemental. Aten neck is THE Vex Thal item (for pretty much all classes), no question in my mind, even if you can't augment it. Agree on TVK earring though, gotta love it, and tanks will love you for choosing it over Aten's earring which they want.  Add TVK pants to that list, chain pants aren't exactly growing on trees for elemental guilds, maybe PoTime but honestly, getting there isn't going to be easy. We have a grand total of 2 elemental pants... a measley 2 (silk) pants out of tons of armor drops overall. My TVK pants are 165hp augmented, nice effect/stats, great resists, really can't go wrong with them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#1F0000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=daliant>daliant</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Qeynos Newbie</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#AAAAAA>(10/22/03 8:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=39.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Weapon Choices...</span><hr size=1> What about me? what do I need? <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.eqfaces.com/photos2/dalsig.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
